{"tid":484302,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為臉鎖挑機蘋果","createTime":"2017-11-30T03:06:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T10:07:56.000Z","uid":31907,"like":3,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"76f9aa5bec338361e0e7ce32e3441d841aceda3c","tid":484302,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:06:37.000Z","msg":"現時只有蘋果iPhone X的Face ID臉部解鎖功能是應用紅外線建立3D認證，成為智能手機新標準。內地手機廠商華為近日則透過「榮耀V10」視頻介紹新技術，宣稱已可透過紅外線投影器，為用戶臉部測繪3D面形。雖然確認解鎖需時10秒，但華為手機的定位點多達30萬個，宣稱比蘋果高10倍。廠方冀明年推出以上功能。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2017/11/30/1713967_e841b5704df5bb871b0b2d98052ac86f_620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F1713967_e841b5704df5bb871b0b2d98052ac86f_620.jpg&h=b99a2db5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f7b8e4d01b91036d9bf37157b3fb3d72d9b6801","tid":484302,"uid":31907,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:07:21.000Z","msg":"確認解鎖需時10秒！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"3cda75b74c39643fb37e55eae8fa933e2c50dd35","tid":484302,"uid":51978,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:07:33.000Z","msg":"確認解鎖需時10秒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26dd0422deb4b07543eff4598ba095f3eaf677eb","tid":484302,"uid":81397,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"10秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cc409d81a06f9f16c53a0f5bf2b3b8de1d8dc7","tid":484302,"uid":31907,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:10:16.000Z","msg":"有幾多秒係upload 去驚城？"},{"pid":"bcf0dcdd2ad5dc0f6c4c964291ec2393fb3e0b6e","tid":484302,"uid":27615,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T03:10:20.000Z","msg":"Apple出咩 都會成為大方向 同當年5s指紋解鎖一樣"},{"pid":"1bccce05984eeaa66c343449589a5d8008959b47","tid":484302,"uid":2857,"like"